Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.65,0:01:26.52,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Delete!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.62,0:01:28.65,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Delete!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.99,0:01:30.89,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Delete!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.37,0:01:43.33,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The average Japanese adult\Nwould say that Teru Mikami
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.50,0:01:46.20,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,was a child with\Na strong sense of justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.27,0:01:48.17,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,One who was able to distinguish\Nright from wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.58,0:01:52.84,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And compared to\Nthe average Japanese...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.91,0:01:54.94,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Teru was also clearly more unfortunate.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.28,0:01:58.41,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He was a person who\Ncontinuously witnessed death.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.27,0:02:54.71,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There is only good and evil\Nin this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.34,0:02:57.21,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That is the first truth that I grasped
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.28,0:03:00.65,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,from watching the world around me\Never since I was young.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.42,0:03:07.45,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All humans are split into two groups,\Nthat of good and evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.26,0:03:13.52,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That held true even in a small world\Nlike elementary school.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.87,0:03:18.50,Death Note Signs/Titles Sm,,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz7.213\pos(365,227)}Class Representative\NThird Year Group A\NTeru Mikami
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.36,0:03:18.26,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,As the class president, no matter what\Nhigh goals I tried to achieve...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.90,0:03:21.96,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,there were always enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.74,0:03:26.90,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop. Stop... Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.55,0:03:32.54,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Evil has to be confronted.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.18,0:03:36.08,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Get him! Get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.62,0:03:39.35,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,At times, it seemed as\Nif justice had lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.16,0:03:45.46,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But I felt happy no matter\Nwhat happened to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.53,0:03:47.46,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.50,0:03:51.47,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Those words from the victims made me
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.80,0:03:54.13,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,want to save them time\Nand time again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.20,0:03:58.83,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't spare any effort for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.21,0:04:00.10,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In the end...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.28,0:04:03.24,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I was able to defend\Nmy sense of justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.81,0:04:07.51,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Just let 'im have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.02,0:04:09.51,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, come on, come on...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.06,0:04:19.72,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.36,0:04:22.66,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That was the case only within\Nthe world of children.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.70,0:04:29.07,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,When I moved to middle school...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.67,0:04:32.70,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The more often I faced evil...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.77,0:04:35.37,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,the more enemies\NI had to face.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.71,0:04:39.61,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Victims became participants...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.08,0:04:41.45,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even observers...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.72,0:04:44.08,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,became influenced by evil\Nand became enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.39,0:04:49.48,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Justice must be served.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.46,0:04:53.39,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I must delete evil\Nin order to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.27,0:05:01.86,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The only one who understood me\Nand was my ally...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.27,0:05:05.24,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,was my mother,\Nwho had raised me by herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.01,0:05:08.57,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No...it should have been my mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.11,0:05:16.48,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Teru... Not everything in the world\Nworks the way you want it to.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.35,0:05:21.29,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please stop. There's no reason\Nfor you to be bullied.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.99,0:05:24.48,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no reason for you\Nto be hurt like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.33,0:05:26.76,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll just look foolish.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.06,0:05:29.22,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing will change,\Nno matter how hard you try...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.30,0:05:32.13,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My mother was wrong...\NShe wasn't right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.77,0:05:36.20,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She was a person who\Nshould not exist...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.31,0:05:39.50,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then a miracle happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.38,0:05:46.21,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The four enemies lost control\Nof their car
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.28,0:05:49.34,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,while joyriding without a license\Nand died.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.85,0:05:52.91,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A bystander was killed...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.02,0:05:55.99,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That bystander was my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.56,0:06:00.72,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The people I denied were deleted.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.63,0:06:04.83,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,At first, I was scared.\NI trembled from my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.20,0:06:06.89,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.74,0:06:11.87,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I was sure there were some people\Nwho were happy due to this elimination.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.24,0:06:13.80,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The victims definitely were...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.18,0:06:18.11,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, almost everyone in my class must\Nhave been glad somewhere in their hearts.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.48,0:06:21.04,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.18,0:06:24.85,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There was a peaceful class...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.79,0:06:31.55,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There was definite retribution\Nfor evil deeds.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.99,0:06:34.98,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It is deserved and needed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.06,0:06:39.33,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Evil must be deleted.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.97,0:06:44.10,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all. Is there anything\Nwrong with this record?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.01,0:06:46.77,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,- My beliefs became stronger...\N- No. Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.84,0:06:49.44,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,with my growth.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.55,0:06:54.28,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There will always be those\Nwho have no reason to exist...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.62,0:06:57.85,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, whose very existence is\Na threat to others.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.69,0:07:03.21,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And the older they are,\Nthe less hope I have to reform them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.36,0:07:05.99,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They can only be deleted.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.57,0:07:12.83,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Surprisingly...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.10,0:07:15.03,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Time and time again,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.10,0:07:17.13,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,whoever I decided should\Nbe deleted was deleted.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.04,0:07:19.13,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Was this a coincidence?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.37,0:07:23.43,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Was I special-?!\NSuch questions aren't important.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.31,0:07:26.40,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Evil must be punished\Nby the heavens...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.81,0:07:31.15,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If it isn't, then someone must bring\Npunishment to that evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.59,0:07:34.38,Death Note Signs/Titles Sm,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(426,429)\fad(834,1168)}Courthouse
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.85,0:07:36.02,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That is why I became a prosecutor.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.62,0:07:38.68,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A prosecutor is the good\Nthat punishes evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.21,0:07:35.72,Death Note Signs/Titles Sm,,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz350.484\move(221,60,93,158,14,2683)\fad(1338,0)}Japanese Constitutional\NDictionary
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.22,0:07:41.51,Death Note Signs/Titles Sm,,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz33.064\move(549,76,363,242,13,4458)}Guide to Japanese\NSentencing
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.93,0:07:41.29,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.50,0:07:43.46,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's when...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.93,0:07:48.27,Death Note Signs/Titles Sm,,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz19.117\move(442,220,460,227,0,3335)}Crime Report\N"Mass Murder of\NVicious Criminals"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.50,0:07:47.33,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,God came before me...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.80,0:07:50.79,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything that had been happening\Naround me until now
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.87,0:07:52.07,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,was not a coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.11,0:07:55.11,Death Note Signs/Titles Sm,,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz16.219\move(297,151,303,167,0,2995)}Who is\Nthe\Ncriminal\Nkiller,\NKira?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.11,0:07:55.11,Death Note Signs/Titles Sm,,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz337.506\move(544,91,533,114,0,2995)}Murders of Vicious\NCriminals Continue
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.11,0:07:55.11,Death Note Signs/Titles Sm,,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz342.453\move(138,289,141,278,0,2995)}Kira Kills a Corrupted Diet Member
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.11,0:07:55.11,Death Note Signs/Titles Sm,,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz21.311\move(475,315,470,301,0,2995)}23 People Die of Heart Attacks
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.71,0:07:54.94,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It was divine justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.24,0:07:59.01,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,God was watching me...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.65,0:08:04.71,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How I did not kneel to evil...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.25,0:08:07.15,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And punished them for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.26,0:08:10.69,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,When I realized that,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.09,0:08:14.08,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I went to the place where I could\Ngrab God's attention the best I could.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.90,0:08:15.73,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.33,0:08:23.13,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,God accepted me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.74,0:08:27.47,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Not only that, but he\Nshared his power with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.21,0:08:33.94,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I must respond to this...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.38,0:08:38.78,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll figure out what Kira wants\Nand do what Kira would do.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.65,0:08:40.35,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Delete.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.89,0:08:46.26,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Delete. Delete. Delete. Delete. Delete.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.49,0:08:51.45,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Delete. Delete. Delete. Delete.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.13,0:08:54.96,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Delete.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.01,0:09:10.71,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikami killed Demegawa\Nbefore I gave the order...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.22,0:09:15.25,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But now there's no one to be\NKira's spokesperson to the world...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.92,0:09:17.91,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do anything in this situation...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.53,0:09:19.65,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you going to do, Mikami?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.46,0:09:23.16,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira isn't saying anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.86,0:09:25.96,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess he's in a situation\Nwhere he can't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.90,0:09:28.43,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But this is an important time...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.04,0:09:31.70,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We need someone to\Nspread Kira's thoughts...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.37,0:09:34.14,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then... I will...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.84,0:09:39.61,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Extra, extra! A new development!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.15,0:09:42.91,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira has chosen a spokesperson\Nto take Demegawa's place.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.78,0:09:44.61,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Take a look!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.25,0:09:49.25,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.49,0:09:54.83,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kiyomi Takada!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.63,0:09:56.43,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.86,0:09:58.96,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Kiyomi Takada of News 6.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.47,0:10:00.76,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Starting today, it is my duty,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.83,0:10:05.83,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,to spread the word of Kira,\Naccurately and quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.97,0:10:08.53,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,NHN's star newscaster, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.21,0:10:12.54,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira has good taste, choosing Takki.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.45,0:10:14.81,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Report everyone's opinions to Kira...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.88,0:10:18.22,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no mistake.\NThis girl is...from Light's college days...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.19,0:10:21.88,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You've dealt with it quickly, Mikami...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.09,0:10:25.65,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But the fact that she and l\Nhad a relationship will quickly be...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.43,0:10:29.76,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No. She's not a bad choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.16,0:10:32.72,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't have thought of her\Nbecause I know her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.80,0:10:34.10,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Things may be getting easier...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.19,0:10:36.19,Death Note Signs/Titles Sm,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(124,311)}Hurricane
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.19,0:10:36.19,Death Note Signs/Titles LG,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,378)}Soon to Hit the United States
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.17,0:10:35.83,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The police are calling for\Ncivilians to evacuate.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.90,0:10:37.53,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikami. I can definitely use him...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.84,0:10:40.14,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to contact him\Nas quickly as possible, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.31,0:10:42.28,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kiyomi Takada...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.18,0:10:46.31,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I spoke to her when we\Nwere on a debate show.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.45,0:10:49.81,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She was a shrewd host, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.58,0:10:52.95,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Her attitude changed\Nwhen Kira was brought up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.92,0:10:59.99,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She has a uniquely rigid way of thinking.\NShe hates crimes and social evils.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.43,0:11:03.76,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I talked to her privately\Nseveral times afterwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.10,0:11:05.40,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She clearly...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.47,0:11:07.23,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,thinks like Kira...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.47,0:11:13.34,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She is the broadcaster who is\Nmost worthy of being Kira's voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.45,0:11:20.38,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kiyomi Takada...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.65,0:11:24.55,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It would be too suspicious to choose\Nan ex-girlfriend as a spokesperson.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.22,0:11:28.31,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There was no sign of Light\Nsending any messages.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.29,0:11:30.98,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I reading too much into this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.73,0:11:33.39,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.99,0:11:35.46,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,About our investigation...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.96,0:11:38.23,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I think we should incorporate\NKiyomi Takada from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.23,0:11:40.63,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,To be honest,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.70,0:11:43.76,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I was quite friendly with\Nher during my college days.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.10,0:11:45.07,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.14,0:11:46.40,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He said it himself?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.54,0:11:48.63,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That means he has no intention\Nof hiding that fact...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.01,0:11:53.14,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If Kira is giving her orders\Nto read messages...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.61,0:11:58.64,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It might be our best option to\Nfind a way to get Kira through her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.56,0:12:07.07,Death Note Signs/Titles Sm,,0000,0000,0000,,{\frx348\fry12\frz26.747\fscx78.75\fscy126.25\move(577,437,510,452,18,7505)}Kiyomi Takada\NChosen as Kira's\NSpokesperson
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.82,0:12:02.98,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But Takki is probably\Nbeing threatened by Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.06,0:12:05.46,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She may be too scared\Nto help us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.09,0:12:07.22,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.49,0:12:12.45,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all right. I know her\Ncell phone number...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.90,0:12:15.89,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She'll meet me if I ask her to.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.47,0:12:20.13,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's some confidence.\NSo typical of you, Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.41,0:12:25.00,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But it'll probably be difficult\Nto get her to help catch Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.78,0:12:28.37,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I talked to her about many things\Nduring college.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.92,0:12:32.25,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She's quite...\Nthe Kira-worshiper.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.79,0:12:36.85,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But we can use that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.86,0:12:40.99,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, even the police\Nsay that they support Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.53,0:12:43.33,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But actually they're doing nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.76,0:12:46.82,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So I'll reveal that I've joined the police
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.03,0:12:51.70,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and ask her what I can do to\Ngive instructions to Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.01,0:12:54.70,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It wouldn't sound like a bad idea\Nto a Kira-supporter like herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.41,0:12:57.00,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Will it go well?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.11,0:12:59.55,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know. But it's worth trying.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.05,0:13:03.41,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I agree, we shouldn't ignore\Na lead that's right before our eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.38,0:13:06.05,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then let's do this tonight, if possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.39,0:13:07.15,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Light!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.92,0:13:11.38,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to listen to your conversation\Nwith Takada.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.46,0:13:13.12,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.39,0:13:15.02,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.30,0:13:19.53,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't know when she may\Ngive us a hint about Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.80,0:13:21.03,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.81,0:13:30.61,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.88,0:13:32.51,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Takada, it's Yagami.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.28,0:13:34.27,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yagami-?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.02,0:13:36.92,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while. What is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.25,0:13:38.15,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Takada...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.42,0:13:39.98,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's something important\NI have to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.79,0:13:42.02,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you meet me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.46,0:13:43.82,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to ask a favor of you...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.46,0:13:45.76,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A favor?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.93,0:13:49.36,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... It might be impossible,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.53,0:13:53.16,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,since you're the woman\Nthe whole world's watching, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.23,0:13:59.40,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think you would have\Ncalled if that wasn't the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.74,0:14:01.40,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.44,0:14:03.70,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Since we left college,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.01,0:14:06.67,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've wanted to tell you,\Nbut I've never had the chance to tell you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.48,0:14:13.11,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But since we've had the chance\Nto connect through our jobs as adults...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.65,0:14:15.71,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't help but feel that it's fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.82,0:14:18.69,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this job?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.23,0:14:21.09,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm with the police right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.40,0:14:24.42,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's also something\NI really wanted to tell you in person...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.30,0:14:28.79,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, the police won't\Ndo anything to betray Kira...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.50,0:14:33.37,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine. I may have to help you,\Ndepending on what you say.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.77,0:14:38.14,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you. I just want you to meet me\Nand listen to what I have to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.55,0:14:41.04,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Somewhere...alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.42,0:14:47.22,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...after the tonight's broadcast\Nis finished...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.66,0:14:51.09,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All right. I'll find a hotel room.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.23,0:14:53.89,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But is that all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.49,0:14:58.06,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yagami, I thought you were living\Nwith Amane.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.90,0:15:00.89,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you still happy together?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.60,0:15:03.09,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.67,0:15:07.54,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The truth is she doesn't have\Nthe brains to be my partner...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.64,0:15:09.54,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mochi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.98,0:15:10.67,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.94,0:15:12.47,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Your cooking is good,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.55,0:15:14.67,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and I appreciate that\Nyou'd do anything for me,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.75,0:15:16.05,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but it's been five days.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.15,0:15:16.81,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.05,0:15:19.75,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Light doesn't know about this,\Ndoes he?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.82,0:15:22.62,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm beginning to get\Na bad feeling about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.76,0:15:23.48,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.62,0:15:25.92,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how much Light trusts me...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.99,0:15:28.29,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think that most people\Nwould think that I might cheat on him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.63,0:15:30.62,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He'll definitely be jealous!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.70,0:15:35.16,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Near and the others told me that\Nthis woman is the Second Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.34,0:15:39.31,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But could this stupid woman\Nreally be?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.01,0:15:45.45,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira hasn't tried to contact me yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.21,0:15:51.21,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If...Kira is in a situation where he\Ncouldn't contact me even if he wanted to...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.65,0:15:53.92,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He'll try to contact Takada first...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.82,0:15:58.79,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Good evening.\NThis is the nine o'clock news.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.43,0:16:03.86,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira's words, which I am to tell you now,\Nare to become the law of this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.46,0:16:08.99,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira will not forgive people\Nwhose existence is deemed a threat.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.14,0:16:13.20,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Additionally, he will not tolerate\Npeople who live wastefully...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.44,0:16:15.74,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and do not use their abilities,\Nfor the good of society.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.11,0:16:18.81,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! Does that mean that\Nhe'll kill lazy people?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.41,0:16:20.51,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're kidding, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.71,0:16:24.65,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're overdoing it, Mikami.\NNo, it's too early.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.09,0:16:27.58,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got to contact Mikami...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.32,0:16:29.81,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Matsuda, how is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.32,0:16:33.09,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, the sound and visuals\Nare great.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.26,0:16:34.19,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No blind spots!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.26,0:16:36.56,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,- The nine o'clock news just ended.\N- See you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.80,0:16:38.89,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Light, I'll be heading back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.30,0:16:39.99,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.90,0:17:15.87,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've wanted to see you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.57,0:17:22.41,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, excuse me. It's just...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.88,0:17:23.84,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please have a seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.38,0:17:31.25,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't seem like it's been that long\Nnow that you're here...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.30,0:17:48.27,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with Light?!\NHe's silent.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.57,0:17:50.66,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He'll look suspicious if he doesn't\Nsay something quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.10,0:17:54.23,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ide...Have you ever been in love?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.31,0:17:54.86,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.08,0:17:55.84,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.04,0:17:57.20,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The mood's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.41,0:17:58.81,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not what I meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.02,0:18:03.98,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.45,0:18:06.11,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.82,0:18:09.79,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikami-?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.46,0:18:11.98,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She said Kira right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.29,0:18:13.88,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is Kira contacting her directly?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.20,0:18:16.13,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You should answer it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.76,0:18:17.49,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.40,0:18:21.66,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello-? No, I'm with a friend...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.07,0:18:23.30,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no one else...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.10,0:18:26.16,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If luck is on my side\NI'll get on the phone...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.77,0:18:29.37,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikami...can you bring me luck?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.21,0:18:31.97,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We decided to meet unexpectedly...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.71,0:18:35.77,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone who could privately\Ncall on Kira's spokesperson...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.75,0:18:38.48,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Pass the phone over to your friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.05,0:18:42.99,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He wants me to give the phone\Nto you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.42,0:18:46.32,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It was right to choose you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.90,0:18:50.29,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She's passed the phone to Light...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.66,0:18:52.39,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's dangerous if it's really Kira!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.37,0:18:54.26,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.04,0:18:56.63,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.21,0:19:02.23,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,November 26?! Five pages?!\NWhat are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.44,0:19:05.17,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,God!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.85,0:19:09.41,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All right... Mikami...\NHow much have you figured out?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.78,0:19:12.08,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't move freely now...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.69,0:19:13.41,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.52,0:19:15.15,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're being watched right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.32,0:19:15.95,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.36,0:19:18.38,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you really Kira?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.13,0:19:21.29,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he asking me to kill right now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.96,0:19:22.95,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn to Sakura TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.20,0:19:25.13,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! Sakura TV?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.73,0:19:26.56,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sakura TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.57,0:19:30.97,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to call back Kira\Nwhatever it takes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.34,0:19:34.10,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He died!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.17,0:19:35.77,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad! He's the real thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.31,0:19:39.68,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,- Mikami...you're better than I expected.\N- Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.86,0:19:44.24,Death Note Signs/Titles Sm,,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz347.455\pos(361,223)}Kira wants to have the room
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.86,0:19:44.24,Death Note Signs/Titles Sm,,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz347.455\pos(321,265)}checked for devices.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.86,0:19:44.24,Death Note Signs/Titles Sm,,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz347.455\pos(322,315)}I'm removing everything
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.86,0:19:44.24,Death Note Signs/Titles Sm,,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz347.455\pos(296,372)}before he sees them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.45,0:19:43.71,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Remove the wiretaps-?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.75,0:19:45.81,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be helped...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.26,0:19:51.22,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What... is the meaning of this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.16,0:19:53.92,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I can talk to you\Nwithout constraints.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.46,0:19:55.12,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.23,0:19:59.69,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, Kiyomi... I'm Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.43,0:20:05.30,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. I'm Kira.\NThat's all...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.87,0:20:09.27,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yagami is...Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.44,0:20:13.71,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen. I won't allow you to ask Kiyomi...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.78,0:20:14.87,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,who I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.75,0:20:18.68,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I leave the rest to you, God...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.02,0:20:21.08,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.72,0:20:24.32,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Kira and that man right now is
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.56,0:20:26.96,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,someone with whom I've shared\NKira's power.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.23,0:20:30.46,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You really are amazing...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.06,0:20:36.83,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the only man I've respected\Nand admired my entire life.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.64,0:20:39.33,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,For you to be Kira...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.44,0:20:41.37,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's too amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.68,0:20:45.91,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,With me...you're...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.48,0:20:48.54,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,going to become the goddess\Nof the new world...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.48,0:20:51.54,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yagami...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.16,0:21:01.82,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Light, are you all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.00,0:21:05.23,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Things went well with Takada.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.73,0:21:10.64,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,From now on, I'll be meeting with her\Nand trying to find Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.87,0:21:14.40,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Delete... Delete... Delete...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.87,0:21:16.47,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Delete, Delete...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.78,0:21:18.30,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Delete. Delete.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.95,0:21:20.00,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Delete!
